{"tid":1343524,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"上環開槍前，示威者與警察談判","createTime":"2019-07-21T18:55:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T03:13:28.000Z","uid":16483,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f19c82555761f11ebc84ebbb18c43faeb7fd7b12","tid":1343524,"uid":16483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:55:20.000Z","msg":"根本佢地開槍前，有議員係同警察個面溝通緊，佢地話要示威者退到去信德。有示威者唔肯，經議員解釋後決定同警察講，示威者退到信德，警察要係原地唔可以推進，直到十二點先開始散，講完都未夠廿秒就無先兆開槍同催淚彈？<br />\n<br />\n我開頭仲覺得唔肯退到信德個班示威者企得太硬，仲係咁話唔會信班差佬，對唔住我知錯了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n經今次後，唔會再相信同班黑警談判係有用，你愈退步佢地就只會更加得寸進尺，香港人必定要反擊，正視呢件事！"},{"pid":"8257918deec337765b9febc311fb25a700b524aa","tid":1343524,"uid":16483,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:58:18.000Z","msg":"今日元朗上環發生既事，必定要追究到底！"},{"pid":"a3545545c6cc8b2d4bb1f8eb6b8814afba07fba4","tid":1343524,"uid":194399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:01:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a09715a62039a8ebb66fc16362f6e5b6ed47aa11","tid":1343524,"uid":281337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:02:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"360dbea5c84363058c81fc5c0e7b9762df28a0f3","tid":1343524,"uid":192824,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:05:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dp4VNKP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdp4VNKP.jpg&h=748d8b7d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b2b04b6bb6926a1287cf88ab79b8e35e1694f9c6","tid":1343524,"uid":268978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:06:18.000Z","msg":"屌你老母推"},{"pid":"91aeedbe15988837a9e089db8fa20ee2bb48d97d","tid":1343524,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:06:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"45305eba076763b126216806b2c3de9f5d5b1b0d","tid":1343524,"uid":16483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:07:1